{"pageProps":{"problem":{"id":"t21-train-2","grade":"7","semester":"up","category":"整式的加减","title":"针对训练2：代入求值","difficulty":3,"tags":["整式","求值"],"content":"当 $x = 2$ 时，代数式 $16ax - 4bx^3 - 2$ 的值为 ______；\n\n已知 $ax^3 + bx + 1 = 5$，则当 $x = -2$ 时，代数式 $ax^3 + bx + 1$ 的值为 ______。","steps":[{"title":"分析奇偶性","content":"设 $f(x) = ax^3 + bx$，这是奇函数，满足 $f(-x) = -f(x)$\n\n由 $f(2) + 1 = 5$，得 $f(2) = 4$","formula":""},{"title":"求目标值","content":"$f(-2) = -f(2) = -4$\n\n所以 $f(-2) + 1 = -4 + 1 = -3$","formula":"\\text{答案：}-3"}]},"id":"t21-train-2"},"__N_SSG":true}